    <note>Yang(2) Dafa [15374] Dafa was the first Wuyi county Yang(2) jinshi, has the same strange character 'fa' as used in the mingzi of Gong(4) Fa [17980], son-in-law of Wuyi county resident Yang(2) Shengqing [24304]. The subsequent Wuyi Yang(2) jinshi are all related, although none are linked to Dafa (who was purged by the Qingyuan coalition). I suspect that all these Yang come from the same lineage, but, for now, do not include them in the dataset. Yang(2) Dafa received his jinshi at the same sitting as Gong(4) Fa's son, Rong [17982]. Wuyi XZ, 7.2a. CBD, 4, 3150.</note>
